<li>Thinking of you and your family during this difficult time.  Your pet will be deeply missed.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and comfort as you grieve the loss of your cherished companion.</li>
<li>I was so saddened to hear about the passing of your wonderful pet.</li>
<li>Your pet held a special place in your hearts, and their memory will live on.</li>
<li>I’m so sorry for your loss.  May precious memories bring you peace.</li>
<li>Your pet brought so much joy to your lives.  They will be dearly missed.</li>
<li>Sending love and strength to you and your family as you say goodbye.</li>
<li>Remembering your pet with fondness and extending heartfelt sympathy.</li>
<li>May the love you shared with your pet bring you comfort during this time.</li>
<li> I can only imagine the pain you must be feeling. Please accept my deepest condolences.</li>
<li> Holding you and your family close in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>Your pet was a truly special companion. Their memory will be a blessing.</li>
<li>Words cannot express the sadness I feel for your loss. May you find peace.</li>
